ta-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_3542424\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Apr 03, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104ned1665703527153.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ned1665703527153.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ned1665703527153.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"ned1665703527153\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Refer to the Selectable Watches buttons to select or deselect items, add watches, or\n      refresh content.</p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ned1665703527153__section_N10015_N10012_N10001\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"ned1665703527153__table_d18467e1_d18468e1_d18469e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ned1665703527153__table_d18467e1_d18468e1_d18469e1__entry__1\">\n Icon\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ned1665703527153__table_d18467e1_d18468e1_d18469e1__entry__2\">\n Action\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ned1665703527153__table_d18467e1_d18468e1_d18469e1__entry__3\">\n Description\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ned1665703527153__table_d18467e1_d18468e1_d18469e1__entry__1\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"ned1665703527153__fig_N10057_N10052_N1004E_N1004B_N1001D_N10019_N10015_N10012_N10001\">\n<img alt=\"Select all items button\" class=\"image\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/selectallwatches.gif?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ned1665703527153__table_d18467e1_d18468e1_d18469e1__entry__2\">Select all items</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ned1665703527153__table_d18467e1_d18468e1_d18469e1__entry__3\">Selects all items in <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Selectable\n                           Watches</span>.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ned1665703527153__table_d18467e1_d18468e1_d18469e1__entry__1\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"ned1665703527153__fig_k5x_dbh_1xb\">\n<img alt=\"Deselect all items button\" class=\"image\" id=\"ned1665703527153__image_l5x_dbh_1xb\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/deselectallwatches.gif?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ned1665703527153__table_d18467e1_d18468e1_d18469e1__entry__2\">Deselect all items</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ned1665703527153__table_d18467e1_d18468e1_d18469e1__entry__3\">Clears all items in <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Selectable\n                           Watches</span>.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ned1665703527153__table_d18467e1_d18468e1_d18469e1__entry__1\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"ned1665703527153__fig_N100AC_N100A7_N100A3_N1004B_N1001D_N10019_N10015_N10012_N10001\">\n<img alt=\"Add watches button\" class=\"image\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/addwatches.gif?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ned1665703527153__table_d18467e1_d18468e1_d18469e1__entry__2\"> Add watches</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ned1665703527153__table_d18467e1_d18468e1_d18469e1__entry__3\">Adds all selected items in the\n                           <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Selectable Watches</span> to the\n                           <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Watches</span> pane of the debugger. <p class=\"p\">You can add\n                           watches even if the debugger is not in control. However, the values of\n                           the added watches are not evaluated until control returns to the\n                           debugger.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ned1665703527153__table_d18467e1_d18468e1_d18469e1__entry__1\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"ned1665703527153__fig_N100DE_N100D9_N100D5_N1004B_N1001D_N10019_N10015_N10012_N10001\">\n<img alt=\"Refresh context button\" class=\"image\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/refreshcontext.gif?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ned1665703527153__table_d18467e1_d18468e1_d18469e1__entry__2\">Refresh context</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ned1665703527153__table_d18467e1_d18468e1_d18469e1__entry__3\">Refreshes the contents of <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Selectable\n                           Watches</span> to the current context of the running application or\n                        component (for instance, after returning from an activated\n                        component).</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3542424\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3542424\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Selectable Watches buttons Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Apr 03, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Refer to the Selectable Watches buttons to select or deselect items, add watches, or refresh content. Icon Action Description Select all items Selects all items in Selectable Watches . Deselect all items Clears all items in Selectable Watches . Add watches Adds all selected items in the Selectable Watches to the Watches pane of the debugger. You can add watches even if the debugger is not in control. However, the values of the added watches are not evaluated until control returns to the debugger. Refresh context Refreshes the contents of Selectable Watches to the current context of the running application or component (for instance, after returning from an activated component). Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}